nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values:
A surreal theatrical scene with five elaborately costumed figures surrounding an abstract chessboard, ocean in the background, dramatic face paint and ornate headpieces, art-fashion performance style. The camera starts at front-view eye level of the chessboard.

CAMERA MOTION:
1. fly up slowly from front view → 
2. smooth crane motion to top-down (90° overhead) view → 
3. camera hovers in top view, stabilizes →
4. slow zoom-in to the knight (horse) chess piece in center →
5. focus lock on knight, details of grime, gold paint, carved texture become clear

ENVIRONMENT:
Outdoor, surreal beach landscape, cloudy blue sky, strong theatrical lighting, eerie calm

STYLE:
artistic, cinematic, avant-garde, dramatic composition, shallow depth of field on final zoom
При ошибках переполнения VRAM необходимо включить blockswap ноды в группах SPEED-UP 1 и 2
